snippet.title: Very funny PETS & ANIMALS! Laughter GUARANTEED - Funny animal ompilation
snippet.description:
Pets and other animals are sooo ool! They make us laugh and smile. Just look how all these dogs, puppies, cats, kittens, goats, turkeys, hamsters, ducks, lizards,... behave, play, fail, make funny sounds, react to different things, get angry and attack... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
